The immediate error you might have faced is : how acdb is correct and abcd not!
Initially you all might have tried this solution:
```
public String removeDuplicateLetters(String s) {
        char[]arr=new char[s.length()];
        for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++) {
            char ch=s.charAt(i);
