**We are going to make use of SET, HASHMAP, AND STACK.**

1.  First we are storing the last index of each and every element
2.  Then we are comparing each and every element wehther it is not present in the visited SET.
3.  IF it is not present.
4.  We are going to run a while loop.
5.  CONDITIONS = 1. STACK NOT EMPTY 2. STACK TOP > CURRENT ELEMENT VALUE 3. HASHMAP VALUE OF I WHIHC IS PRESENT IN STACK > CURRENT ELEMENT VALUE.
6.  IF  all conditions satsify then we are going to remove the element from the visited set, which is the element which we are going to pop out from the stack.
7.  If condition is not satisfied then we have to APPEND the current element value into the stack and also ADD the value into the set.
8.  Finally we have to JOIN all the avlues present in the stack into the set.


